  "body": "<h1 style=\"font-size:60px;\"align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cWF6Bwm.png\"></h1>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:25px\" align=\"center\">Adds flying whales to the game!</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:25px\" align=\"center\">These whales are passive and spawn in the Plains biome!</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:25px\" align=\"center\">They can be tamed with cod and ridden to explore the surroundings.</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:25px\" align=\"center\">They rarely drop the \"Artifact of Levitation\", which grants its user levitation!</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:25px\" align=\"center\">This mod won't be updated!</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\"><img align=\"middle\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rTa7vKa.png\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\"><img align=\"middle\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8eWeN3P.png\" width=\"344\" height=\"72\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modfest.net/\"><img align=\"middle\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/i19CiMx.png\" width=\"344\" height=\"72\"></a></p>",
